guards: if we want perform an logic when user loads 
or unloads a page or a view or a module, we can use guards

canActivate: it loads when we try to activate the page
canActivateChild:  scope is at view(partial) level
Resolve: used to prefetch the data
canDeactivate: when user unloads the page without saving his work, we can prompt the user when he taps out
CanLoad: we can provide restriction at module level